# Methodology

## Data Collection

Our data collection process consisted of three phases: (1) GitHub repository discovery through systematic search queries, (2) indicator-based pre-selection using LiaScript-specific heuristics, and (3) AI-based validation to filter false positives. This multi-stage approach balances broad coverage (high recall) with precision.

### Phase 1: GitHub Repository Discovery

We conducted a systematic search of GitHub using the GitHub API (v3), combining repository-level and code-level searches with quality-ranked queries.

